<H1>Examples of changing the sort order</H1>

<P>To sort a file in dictionary order:</P>

<PRE WIDTH=80>   <STRONG>sort -d +1 -2names &gt; orders</STRONG>
</PRE>

<P>Lines in the file <SAMP>names</SAMP> are sorted on field 2 into
dictionary order and the result placed in the file 
<SAMP>orders</SAMP>.</P>

<HR>

<P>To sort a file in month order:</P>

<PRE WIDTH=80>   <STRONG>sort -M +2 -3 -o breakdown orders</STRONG>
</PRE>

<P>Lines in the file <SAMP>orders</SAMP> are sorted on field 3 into month
order and the result placed in the file <SAMP>breakdown</SAMP>.</P>

